{
  "stem": "1496.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we-- the food, number one, food was rationed in Plaszow, and was very little.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Let me just give you an idea.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The ration for the day was in the morning, we had a bowl of coffee, so-called coffee.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At noontime, we had a bowl of soup, which most of the time was very watery, once in awhile, depends on what was available, what the rations were.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Sometime was a little bit thicker.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But most of the time, was very watery.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And at the evening, we got a loaf of bread, which had to be divided into six portions, into six people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And once in a while, we got some sugar or margarine, and that's all.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were constantly hungry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You cannot imagine the hunger pain when you're always dreaming how to get something into your stomach.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Beside-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] beside being hungry, we were constantly exposed to harassment, to selection, to beating, to hanging, to execution.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In this camp, there was no gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There were no crematorium.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But all the executions were done by shooting most of the time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they were all buried in mass graves.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Well, the working-- whoever worked in the shop, like I did, had a little bit better.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But the people working on the outside, building the roads or building barracks, and also throwing-- carrying stone from one area to another, they were constantly exposed to harassment and even to be executed, because if you-- they were watched by SS people and Ukrainian people.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they only were looking for-- for you to make some kind of mistake in order to shoot you.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
